# truu-copilot-kit merge protection

# Prevents git subtree pull from overwriting files you've enriched with project-specific content.

# Register the driver once per machine: git config --global merge.ours.driver true

# Protect enriched generic skills (uncomment paths you've customised past the kit baseline):

# .github/skills/architecture/SKILL.md merge=ours

# .github/skills/context-engineering/SKILL.md merge=ours

# .github/skills/debugging/SKILL.md merge=ours

# .github/skills/security/SKILL.md merge=ours

# .github/skills/testing/SKILL.md merge=ours

# .github/copilot-recursive-template.md merge=ours
